SABC COO Chris Maroleng has been found guilty of three of four charges, some of which relate to his alleged role in the controversial reappointment of sports presenter Robert Marawa back to the SABC. Maroleng had been subjected to a disciplinary process since January this year. The sanction for his alleged indiscretions will be delivered at a later date. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD